  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the prevalence and predictors of pituitary
      dysfunction, as well as secondary out-come in patients with traumatic brain injury or
      spontaneous subarachnoidal haemorrhages.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
